{"tid":1652781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[非割蓆] 鶳藍絲出手請分輕重","createTime":"2019-10-13T20:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T21:09:29.000Z","uid":178677,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a795072517e8144b5fcd24b01b24191dd2f8f9f","tid":1652781,"uid":178677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:11:07.000Z","msg":"鶳黑警我十分支持，但鶳藍絲可摸以分程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢兩日有做twitter文宣嘅人，應該都見到對家瘋傳緊幾條女人藍蛆被鶳嘅片，而呢幾條片藍蛆都係口角only 屌下手足但冇郁手<br />\n之後手足就開遮噴漆同推推拉拉<br />\n我地就睇到好爽，但真心好難喺國際線解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 有外國人見到，本身都支持我地抗爭，但retweet咗話我地crazy打女人<br />\n老實講 咁多5毛咁多bot，twitter 戰線又唔多人，好難洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後發夢遇到動口不動手嘅藍絲廢老，就冷處理咗佢地啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然佢地郁手一定要還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aae5a99dde5253bd3cbe9102ab76c1e14f233a2","tid":1652781,"uid":154186,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:17:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 次撚次都唔信手足 冇片睇都知對面冇郁手係唔會鶳 次次都要等啲前傳出嚟先信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938189d100830f995be409cfdbde6b97f6baec02","tid":1652781,"uid":178677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:18:07.000Z","msg":"國際線雖然係副線，但都係重要嘅副線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61de757ae3410bb0893573fb55b0d8a40fbf2ef","tid":1652781,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:21:23.000Z","msg":"一開頭咪又話打錯馬蹄露 之後見到邊個出手先啦"},{"pid":"2c7e2cc5201d7a796ca43c5e76cf7f728db92592","tid":1652781,"uid":215501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T21:07:20.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"ded0fd336250434a12467e7c8840fb8d5548cfee","tid":1652781,"uid":178677,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T21:06:09.00